    "Details": "The MGP-86 is an unconventional Capellan scout built from a patchwork of sourced and stolen technology. Stealth armor powered by a Guardian ECM keeps it invisible to sensors while a Partial Wing stolen from Clan Jade Falcon extends jump distance well beyond standard capability. Twin ER Medium Lasers provide combat punch and an MML 3 with both ammunition types covers additional range brackets when the situation demands it.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stubble Wings</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
